main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Colfax, Iowa on October 13, 1956 at 23:15.
interesting points: The observation was made using radar, indicating a technological aspect to the sighting.
The object was described as having round shape and white, flashing red, green, and white lights.
The object was observed moving slowly with white light.
The report suggests a possible prosaic explanation, with the comment 'Probably is Balloon.'
No photograph or image was included in the report.
sighted object: a round UFO with flashing red, green, and white lights
